                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ta grandeur me remplit d'effroi,\nPolichinelle ! — Réponds-moi.\nIl paraît que tu bats ta femme."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Eh ! oui, quelquefois je l'entame !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Oui, je la rosse, je la bats,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Et même, on m'entend de là-bas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Quand, féroce comme un Cosaque,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Je lui tombe sur la casaque",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et de cent coups je lui fais don.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh ! oui, quelquefois je l'entame !\nOui, je la rosse, je la bats,\nEt même, on m'entend de là-bas,\nQuand, féroce comme un Cosaque,\nJe lui tombe sur la casaque\nEt de cent coups je lui fais don."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Mais, lui demandes-tu pardon ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais, lui demandes-tu pardon ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Il serait beau que je le fisse !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il serait beau que je le fisse !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Alors, dis, par quel artifice",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Es-tu cependant adoré ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Alors, dis, par quel artifice\nEs-tu cependant adoré ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "C'est que mon habit est doré.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est que mon habit est doré."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Madame, dit-on, se révolte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Madame, dit-on, se révolte"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Parfois. Eh ! oui. Par l'archivolte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "De mon palais ! tu dis fort bien.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Parfois elle rompt son lien.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Parfois. Eh ! oui. Par l'archivolte\nDe mon palais ! tu dis fort bien.\nParfois elle rompt son lien."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Ces jours derniers, émancipée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "La dame s'était échappée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Par un élan bien réussi !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ces jours derniers, émancipée,\nLa dame s'était échappée\nPar un élan bien réussi !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Vrai Dieu ! qu'elle était belle ainsi,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Mon Espagnole, ma Chimène !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Elle tranchait de l'inhumaine !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Elle portait d'un air mignon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "La rose rouge à son chignon,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Et, fière, elle frémissait toute",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Dans l'air libre, ayant une goutte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "De sang de taureau dans le cœur !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vrai Dieu ! qu'elle était belle ainsi,\nMon Espagnole, ma Chimène !\nElle tranchait de l'inhumaine !\nElle portait d'un air mignon\nLa rose rouge à son chignon,\nEt, fière, elle frémissait toute\nDans l'air libre, ayant une goutte\nDe sang de taureau dans le cœur !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Cependant, te voilà vainqueur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Parle-moi, beau chanteur de gammes :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Quel charme en toi dompte les dames ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Car ta bosse est pleine de vent",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Par derrière, aussi par devant ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Et, comme tu fus un ivrogne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "On voit fleurir ta rouge trogne.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Pour le reste, nous t'égalons !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Cependant, te voilà vainqueur.\nParle-moi, beau chanteur de gammes :\nQuel charme en toi dompte les dames ?\nCar ta bosse est pleine de vent\nPar derrière, aussi par devant ;\nEt, comme tu fus un ivrogne,\nOn voit fleurir ta rouge trogne.\nPour le reste, nous t'égalons !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "C'est parce que j'ai des galons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est parce que j'ai des galons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Parlons franc. Tout le jour tu vides",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Les pots, de tes lèvres avides ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Et, trouvant que la soif te nuit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Tu les vides encor la nuit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Ta conduite est fort excentrique :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Au retour, tu prends une trique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Et, délibérément, tu bats",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Le manteau, la robe et les bas",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "De madame Polichinelle.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Qui donc fait que la péronnelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Consent à ces jeux effrénés ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Parlons franc. Tout le jour tu vides\nLes pots, de tes lèvres avides ;\nEt, trouvant que la soif te nuit,\nTu les vides encor la nuit.\nTa conduite est fort excentrique :\nAu retour, tu prends une trique\nEt, délibérément, tu bats\nLe manteau, la robe et les bas\nDe madame Polichinelle.\nQui donc fait que la péronnelle\nConsent à ces jeux effrénés ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 14,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "La pourpre — que j'ai sur mon nez !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La pourpre — que j'ai sur mon nez !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 15,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Bref, ayant mis à sec une outre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Tu vides l'autre, et passes outre ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Tu nous montres, étant fort laid,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Des cheveux plus blancs que du lait,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Et, de plus, tu deviens obèse.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "D'où vient que ta femme te baise",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi qu'un héros de roman ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Apprends-moi donc quel talisman",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Fait qu'une dame si jolie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Supporte la triste folie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "De ton caractère immoral ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Bref, ayant mis à sec une outre,\nTu vides l'autre, et passes outre ;\nTu nous montres, étant fort laid,\nDes cheveux plus blancs que du lait,\nEt, de plus, tu deviens obèse.\nD'où vient que ta femme te baise\nAinsi qu'un héros de roman ?\nApprends-moi donc quel talisman\nFait qu'une dame si jolie\nSupporte la triste folie\nDe ton caractère immoral ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 16,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "C'est mon chapeau de général !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est mon chapeau de général !"
        }
    ],
